Lettuce Cloak
Wondrous Item, uncommon
Woven from big, magical lettuce leaves, the lettuce cloak
is a popular piece of gear among novice adventurers. Whenever you are targeted with a nonmagical 
weapon attack that you are aware of while wearing this cloak, you can use your reaction to increase 
your AC by 1 against the attack.
Mask of Eternal Might
Wondrous Item, very rare (requires attunement)
