alluring, emitting a captivating glow that draws in anyone who gazes upon them. These masks are 
both a blessing and a curse created by the ancient agents of the God of Trickery (p. 56).
When you wear this mask, all of your ability scores increase by 2. You don't need to eat, drink or 
